493
00:36:25,520 --> 00:36:26,920
Bakit ka nagmamadaling
madischarge?

494
00:36:28,040 --> 00:36:30,280
Walang kwenta
ang manatili sa ospital.

495
00:36:30,960 --> 00:36:32,120
Kung nalaman ni Da Qiong,

496
00:36:32,240 --> 00:36:33,440
maghihinala siya.

497
00:36:34,280 --> 00:36:36,040
Salamat sa lahat
sa panahong ito.

498
00:36:36,800 --> 00:36:37,800
Mr. Wu.

499
00:36:37,801 --> 00:36:38,880
Gustong makita ka ng isang kliyente.

500
00:36:39,200 --> 00:36:40,200
WHO?

501
00:36:40,440 --> 00:36:41,440
G. Wang Shuo.

502
00:36:44,200 --> 00:36:45,520
- Wang Shuo?
- Oo.

503
00:36:48,080 --> 00:36:49,080
Papasukin mo siya.

504
00:36:49,680 --> 00:36:50,680
Okay.

505
00:36:59,720 --> 00:37:00,720
Hello.

506
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:01,840
Ako si Wang Shuo.

507
00:37:11,040 --> 00:37:12,440
(Bonus Clip)

508
00:37:13,160 --> 00:37:14,279
Hindi na ako naglalaro.

509
00:37:14,280 --> 00:37:15,359
Maglaro ng isa pang round.

510
00:37:15,360 --> 00:37:16,640
Ano ang dapat nating laruin kung gayon?

511
00:37:16,720 --> 00:37:17,720
I will go easy on you
sa next round.

512
00:37:17,721 --> 00:37:19,400
Hindi kita matatalo. Seryoso.

513
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:20,760
Humanap ng ibang mapaglalaruan.

514
00:37:21,840 --> 00:37:23,480
Hindi na ako naglalaro. huminto ako.
